comments.body: Wow! Awesome find! You don't often see wild pics of this one!
Nominated for SA Observation of the month  (July) for the first of and photographic quality.
Really cool!! not often you see pictures of this snake
Spectacular!  Thanks for the head's up, Mike.  @catenatus
@tiwane  I think you "owe me one", haha!  : )

Nice find, thanks for sharing @bartwursten, this is iNaturalist's Observation of the Day! We've posted it to our Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram accounts. Thanks for the heads up @michael_jacobi and @bobbyfingers. However, just a note that messages are often safer, as they're less likely to be lost than mentions.
